casebody.data:
PEOPLE
v.
FORNEY S238013 Supreme Court of California December 14, 2016

Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Werdegar, Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

**1241The petition for review is granted. Further action in this matter is deferred pending consideration and disposition of a related issue in People v. Garcia, S218197 (see Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.512(d)(2) ), or pending further order of the court. Submission of additional briefing, pursuant to **1242California Rules of Court, rule 8.520, is deferred pending further order of the court.
